'''[[Cathar/Legends|Cathar]] city-trees''' were located on the [[Planet/Legends|planet]] [[Cathar (location)/Legends|Cathar]]. The [[Homeworld/Legends|native]] [[Species/Legends|species]] of the planet, the Cathar, lived in these trees. A memorial was built into one of these for [[Sylvar]], a [[Jedi Knight/Legends|Jedi Knight]] during the [[Great Sith War/Legends|Great Sith War]].

